      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "The Tiger Buckets Collection: A Glimpse into Malbon's Vision",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At the core of the Tiger Buckets Collection is a celebration of individuality and self-expression on the golf course. Malbon Golf is known for fusing art, culture, and sport, and this collection exemplifies that ethos perfectly. The collection offers a variety of apparel pieces that seamlessly blend performance with style, catering to the modern golfer who values both aesthetics and functionality.</p><p>Key pieces in the collection include:</p><ul><li><strong>Tiger Buckets Polos</strong>: Available in colours like black, natural, and hunter green, these polos are crafted from moisture-wicking fabric to keep you cool during your game. The standout feature is the elegant Tiger Buckets logo, subtly embroidered on the chest.</li><li><strong>Bucket Hats</strong>: The bucket hats, with their laid-back style, not only offer sun protection but also add a playful yet stylish touch to your golf attire. The bold tiger design on the hats reflects Malbon's signature flair for streetwear-inspired golf fashion.</li><li><strong>Hoodies and T-Shirts</strong>: The Tiger Buckets hoodies and t-shirts provide a comfortable yet trendy option for casual days. Made from high-quality fabrics, these pieces transition seamlessly from the golf course to everyday wear.</li></ul>"
          }
        }
