        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The Tiger Buckets Collection stands out for its careful attention to detail and use of premium materials. Whether you're wearing a polo or a hoodie, each piece is designed to not only look great but also perform well during your golf rounds.</p><ul><li><strong>Moisture-Wicking Fabrics: </strong>One of the key features of the Tiger Buckets polos is their moisture-wicking technology. This ensures that you remain cool and dry, even during intense games in warm weather. The fabrics are breathable and lightweight, making them ideal for long hours on the course.</li><li><strong>Tailored Fit: </strong>Another hallmark of the collection is its tailored fit. The polos are designed to provide a flattering silhouette without sacrificing comfort. This balance between style and performance is perfect for golfers who want to look sharp without compromising on mobility.</li></ul><p>The combination of moisture-wicking fabrics, sleek designs, and high-quality construction makes the Tiger Buckets Collection a standout option for golfers who prioritise both fashion and performance.</p>"
          }
        }
