          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>One of the most appealing aspects of the Tiger Buckets Collection is its versatility. The pieces are designed to be mixed and matched, offering endless styling possibilities both on and off the golf course. Here are some tips for creating the perfect look with your Tiger Buckets gear:</p><ul><li><strong>On the Course: </strong>Pair the Tiger Buckets Polo in Hunter Green with neutral-coloured golf trousers and a matching Tiger Buckets bucket hat for a cohesive, stylish look. Complete the outfit with white golf shoes for a clean finish.</li><li><strong>Off the Course: </strong>Transition your look to a casual outing by swapping out your golf trousers for tailored shorts or denim. Throw on a Tiger Buckets hoodie over your polo for an effortlessly cool vibe. The bucket hat adds a touch of streetwear flair, making it ideal for post-game wear.</li></ul><p>With its sleek designs and adaptable pieces, the Tiger Buckets Collection allows golfers to express their style both on the green and beyond.</p>"
          }
        }
